$sudo apt-get install openjdk-8-jdk
Download Floodlight controller from this link https://drive.google.com/file/d/1j6aFv6msgdKmPrnMm-cOEO055BtKOPEi/view?usp=sharing
you can run
$cd floodlight
$git submodule init
$git submodule update
$ant
to check if it build successfully
then run $ ./floodlight.sh to start the controller
after that run ./flow.sh to add flow rules continously based on ModSecurity Alerts
